<br>
So explain to me how an open-ended, open-dollar, unrestricted contract like the one Haliburton was awarded (which they have used to invoice almost one BILLION dollars to the American taxpayer so far) would in any way ensure the lowest prices?<br>
<br>
Doesn't Haliburton have a duty to their sharehold to maximize profit?  I am certain you have touted the &quot;corporation has a duty to the shareholder&quot; argument in this forum.  With the duty to maximize shareholder profit that Haliburton has, why would they even try to be the lowest price when they have no price restrictions and no contract ceilings?<br>
<br>
Dick Cheney has hundreds of thousands of stock options in Haliburton.  All he has to do is wait until he isn't in office to cash them out.<br>
<br>
Rumor has it there is a good chance he won't be running for VP in 2004 because Bush will want to hand-pick his successor.  Expect Cheney to cash out those options as soon as the conflict-of-interest restrictions are lifted. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showMessageRange?topicID=215.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showMessageRange?topicID=215.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showMessageRange?topicID=215.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showMessageRange?topicID=215.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showMessageRange?topicID=215.topic&start=101&stop=119>6</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showPrevMessage?topicID=215.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showNextMessage?topicID=215.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=215.topic&index=60><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.threadControl?topicID=215.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=215.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to re